contexts.context: "I am Kena <mark>Warfel</mark> Tomasin, and I can prove that Akatosh, Nirn,...
...that Akatosh, Nirn, and Oblivion are one," said <mark>Warfel</mark>, writing out the mathematical formula that showed it was so....
...out the mathematical formula, which proved correct, and Kena <mark>Warfel</mark> Tomasin vaporized on the spot.
